title: Netanyahu Vows to Cut Israel’s Reliance on U.S. Military Aid
summary_full: Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu blamed some soldiers’ deaths in the Gaza war on a lack of ammunition caused by a pause in American weapon deliveries during President Biden’s term.
